Responsibilities
Manage daily operation of multiple e-commerce channels including orders, products, contents and promotion;
Responsible for uploading & maintenance of all listed products;
Monitor stock level to avoid OOS of platforms;
Handle ad hoc operation tasks about eCommerce channels per request;
Liaise and coordinate with business partners and related departments on day-to-day business operations.

