Diploma or above with minimum of 3 years relevant working experience;
Experience in operating CN and Oversea platforms is highly preferred;
Proficiency in Microsoft Excel and Word;
Excellent in both written and spoken Chinese and English;
High level of flexibility and adaptability with good problem-solving skills.

