About Zeek
Zeek is the brand name under Kin Shun Information Technology Limited which incorporated in 2019. Zeek aims to provide smart logistics, SaaS solutions and online / offline integrated instant delivery service for Hong Kong and Southeast Asia market, meeting their needs for food & parcel delivery and last-mile logistics.

We strive for building an excellent delivery experience by adopting big data and artificial intelligence. With existing business in Hong Kong, Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand and Vietnam, we will continue to expand our business to Southeast Asia countries and regions like Taiwan, Philippines and Indonesia in near future.

Responsibilities: 

Represent headquarter to oversee operational and financial KPIs of Food & Quick Commerce business across multiple SEA markets, and provide executional inputs to local operations teams in optimizing operational efficiency and service level
Take lead in operational planning for launch of new markets or services in existing markets;
Maintain right sets of indicators and reports for effective analysis on services and operations, and also identifying improvement opportunities for Hong Kong and overseas markets;
Facilitate local operations team to diagnose existing issues in operations and the execution of initiatives by cooperating with various internal parties and external partners;
Take ownership on urgent issues in operations and take timely actions;
Keep abreast of the market’s leading practices and understand competitors’ operating models to ensure company’s practice has its competitive advantages;
Share knowledge and leading practices in operations in Headquarter for local operations teams to take reference;
Develop standard operating procedures and guidelines for overseas markets;
Develop BI report templates for operations management and monitoring across markets;
Perform ad-hoc duties assigned by Management

Requirements:

Degree holder in any disciplines; 
Minimum 4 years of experience in operations management, project management or consulting, with experiences in start-ups, logistic platforms, F&B or e-commerce sectors preferred;
Strong planning and analytical skills with strong business sense and problem-solving skill;
Sensitive to numbers and capable in scientific analysis, candidates with BI reporting experience have advantage;
Proactive and able to work under pressure with multi-tasking ability;
Independent, self-motivated, detail-oriented, good team player and able to work in a fast paced and dynamic working environment;
Good command of written and spoken English, Cantonese and Mandarin;
Proficient in MS applications, e.g. PowerPoint, Excel and Word

